sequenceDiagram
    participant SIM as Simulator
    participant DS as DeviceStore
    participant ES as EnergyStore
    participant SB as SocketBroadcaster
    participant FE as Frontend (React)

    loop Every 5 seconds
        SIM->>DS: applyBatch(statusUpdates)
        DS->>DS: update in-memory state
        DS-->>SB: emit devices:changed
        SIM->>ES: record(totalWatts)
        ES->>ES: integrate energy (trapezoidal)
        SB->>FE: socket.emit("devices:update", snapshot)
        SB->>FE: socket.emit("usage:update", {powerWatts, energyWh})
    end

    Note over FE: React state updates → re-render
